default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAs a campaigning organisation of blind and partially sighted people, we fight for the rights of people with sight loss in each of the UK’s four countries. Our priorities are to:
